---
title: Black Bean and Farro Salad with Apple, Avocado and Radish
description: When farro and black beans join forces, the result is a protein-packed force to be reckoned with. We rounded out this delicious, healthy, and simple meatless dinner with creamy avocado, crisp apples, and crunchy radishes.
